=======

A River called Titas concerns the tumultuous lives of people in fishing villages
along the banks of the Titas River in pre-Partition East Bengal. Focusing on the
tragic intertwining fates of a series of fascinating characters Ghatak tells the
poignant story of an entire community's vanishing way of life.
Made soon after Bangladesh became an independent nation, A River Called Titas is
a grand epic.

